{"tid":1419692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家諗諗罷工既目的","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:30:21.000Z","uid":78648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e280408a654b4458f4d721658f0989de614922c8","tid":1419692,"uid":78648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:18:15.000Z","msg":"罷工既目的就係想癱瘓香港經濟 <br />\n令到政府一定要聽取民意<br />\n如果想癱瘓經濟又唔想同d狗開戰<br />\n咁最直接一定係癱瘓機場<br />\nD狗唔敢放催淚彈<br />\n和理非又可以參與<br />\n而家已經有11個地區對香港發出旅遊警示<br />\n再咁落去旅客消費減少幾多政府自己心知<br />\n所以大家記住8月9日一定要去機場呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開始時間： 2019年8月9日下午1 點起<br />\n地點 ： 一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n1. 不申請不反對通知書<br />\n2. 和平靜坐，不衝擊不破壞不入禁區<br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"810b928721721314c91f79888b9c9968a1c774c9","tid":1419692,"uid":78648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:19:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c3bdfeb6fe8a54847d93a1abf5b39ba95ebfb3b","tid":1419692,"uid":78648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72e49bdf684e4283914f2c5d306a616e5acf3ccd","tid":1419692,"uid":78648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cAzSox.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cAzSox.png&h=ad68287c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3719df2f4397c020424c3a183a851119f251a7f","tid":1419692,"uid":78648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:26:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a686be1348139a6cb62bb4f4c6a1fe099060da8","tid":1419692,"uid":78648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}